  <refnamediv>
    <refname>xpause</refname>
    <refpurpose> suspend Scilab</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <title>Calling Sequence</title>
    <synopsis>xpause(microsecs)</synopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para><literal>xpause</literal> suspends the current process for the number of microseconds
    specified by the argument. The actual suspension time may
    be longer because of other activities in
    the system, or because of the time spent in processing the
    call.</para>
  </refsection>
  <refsection>
    <title>Authors</title>
    <para>J.Ph.C.  </para>
  </refsection>
